						<div class="right">
							<p>Ludum enables you and your team to keep winning and achieving better results through the power of performance data, better organisation and smooth communication.</p>
							<p>Empower athletes to train at the right intensity levels, helping to prevent injury and illness and get the edge that sets the winners apart from others, while a coach has a convenient way of adapting training plans to achieve high performance and a steady athlete development pace.</p>
						</div>
